@startuml
title Activity Diagram - Get Job Recommendations

start
:Applicant views recommendations;
:Frontend sends GET /api/applicant/recommendations with Bearer token and filters;
:Server verifies JWT token and role=applicant;
:Server finds applicant by user_id in database;
:Server sends POST request to AI Service (Server-2) /api/recommendations;
:AI Service analyzes applicant profile and returns recommended jobs;
:Server returns 200 with recommendations;
:Frontend displays recommended jobs to applicant;
stop

@enduml
